### API surface

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Create account |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Get JWT token |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Current user |
| GET | `/api/topics` | List topics |
| POST | `/api/topics` | Create topic (admin) |
| GET | `/api/proposals` | List proposals (filterable by status, topic) |
| POST | `/api/proposals` | Create proposal |
| GET | `/api/proposals/{id}` | Get proposal |
| PATCH | `/api/proposals/{id}` | Update proposal (author, draft only) |
| POST | `/api/proposals/{id}/advance` | Advance proposal status |
| GET | `/api/proposals/{id}/results` | Tally + time-series snapshots |
| GET | `/api/proposals/{id}/my-vote` | How the current user's vote resolves |
| GET | `/api/delegations` | List my delegations |
| PUT | `/api/delegations` | Set/update delegation (cycle-checked upsert) |
| DELETE | `/api/delegations/{topic_id}` | Revoke delegation |
| GET | `/api/delegations/graph` | My delegation neighbourhood |
| PUT | `/api/delegations/precedence` | Set topic priority ordering |
| POST | `/api/proposals/{id}/vote` | Cast direct vote |
| DELETE | `/api/proposals/{id}/vote` | Retract direct vote |
| GET | `/api/users/{id}` | Public profile |
| GET | `/api/users/{id}/delegation-tree` | Delegation tree for a user |
| GET | `/api/users/{id}/votes` | Public vote history |
| POST | `/api/admin/seed` | Load demo scenario |
| POST | `/api/admin/time-simulation` | Take a tally snapshot at a simulated time |
| GET | `/api/admin/delegation-graph` | System-wide delegation graph |
| WS | `/ws/proposals/{id}` | Live tally updates |

