### Demo scenarios (seed data)

**Scenario A ‚Äî Healthcare Reform Act** (`POST /api/admin/seed` with `{"scenario": "healthcare"}`)
- 20 users + Dr. Chen + EconExpert
- Proposal tagged `healthcare` + `economy`
- Users 1‚Äì10: healthcare > economy precedence ‚Üí follow Dr. Chen ‚Üí **YES**
- Users 11‚Äì15: economy > healthcare precedence ‚Üí follow EconExpert ‚Üí **NO**
- Users 16‚Äì18: direct votes (YES / NO / ABSTAIN), overriding their delegations
- Demonstrates topic precedence and direct-vote override

**Scenario B ‚Äî Environmental Budget Allocation** (`POST /api/admin/seed` with `{"scenario": "environment"}`)
- Delegate A (no vote) sub-delegates to Delegate B (votes YES)
- Group 1 (`accept_sub`): chain follows to Delegate B ‚Üí **YES**
- Group 2 (`revert_direct`): flagged, vote unresolved
- Group 3 (`abstain`): vote not cast
- Demonstrates all three `chain_behavior` modes

