### Tests ‚Äî 18/18 passing

| Test | What it covers |
|------|---------------|
| `test_direct_vote_beats_delegation` | Direct vote overrides any delegation |
| `test_delegation_used_when_no_direct_vote` | Delegate's vote used when user hasn't voted |
| `test_no_vote_when_no_delegation_no_direct` | Returns None with no delegation and no vote |
| `test_topic_precedence_highest_priority_wins` | Highest-priority topic's delegate is used |
| `test_topic_precedence_second_priority_wins` | Second topic wins when it has higher priority |
| `test_global_delegation_fallback` | Global delegation used when no topic-specific one |
| `test_topic_delegation_takes_precedence_over_global` | Topic-specific beats global |
| `test_chain_accept_sub_follows_sub_delegate` | accept_sub traverses one extra hop |
| `test_chain_accept_sub_returns_none_when_sub_delegate_also_absent` | Chain dead-end returns None |
| `test_chain_revert_direct_returns_none` | revert_direct returns None |
| `test_chain_abstain_returns_none` | abstain returns None |
| `test_cycle_prevention_simple` | A‚ÜíB, B‚ÜíA blocked |
| `test_cycle_prevention_transitive` | A‚ÜíB‚ÜíC, C‚ÜíA blocked |
| `test_no_false_positive_cycle` | A‚ÜíB, A‚ÜíC allowed |
| `test_cycle_prevention_per_topic` | Cycle check is per-topic graph |
| `test_tally_updates_when_delegation_changes` | Re-delegating mid-window changes tally |
| `test_compute_tally` | Full tally aggregation across all users |
| `test_self_delegation_cycle` | A‚ÜíA blocked |

